+/**
+ * SARSA (State-Action-Reward-State-Action)
+ *
+ * On-policy TD learning algorithm with:
+ * - Epsilon-greedy exploration
+ * - State hashing for continuous states
+ * - Expected SARSA variant (optional)
+ * - Eligibility traces (SARSA-lambda)
+ *
