+ * Performance Targets:
+ * - Adaptation: <0.05ms
+ * - Pattern retrieval: <1ms
+ * - Learning step: <10ms
+ *
+ * Supported Modes:
+ * - real-time: Sub-millisecond adaptation (2200 ops/sec)
